I herewith take the liberty to announce the recent start of a new mailing 
list called

                ``The Artificial Intelligence Research Club''

This mailing list will discuss how to practically construct an AI that should 
become self-aware.  

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The purpose of the mailing list is to serve as a sounding board, and as a 
medium to exchange technical information and through which possibly to 
construct individual cooperations, to people who are themselves engaged in     
constructing (parts of) a self-aware AI. 

