Okay, so I'm still puzzled why you express such confidence that
extraterrestrial life is common, rather than regarding it an
open question. Gathering this information is difficult, it's
clear that we need to study the actual composition and evolution
of the galaxy much more before we will be able to close a large
question like this.

> > In the absence of this information, I'm comfortable with the
